  "content": "<p>Hold onto your hats, folks! La Mafia Heist is not for the faint of heart. With high volatility and an RTP of 96.35%, this game is perfect for those who like to live dangerously and chase those big payouts. But be warned, this game is like the Mafia - it takes no prisoners!</p>"
